     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n      <p class=\"res-header-id\">\n        <b>Generated Narrative: CodeSystem risk-assessment-method-example</b>\n      </p>\n      <a name=\"risk-assessment-method-example\"> </a>\n      <a name=\"hcrisk-assessment-method-example\"> </a>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\">\n        <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Last updated: 2021-01-05T10:01:24.148+11:00</p>\n      </div>\n      <p>This case-sensitive code system \n        <code>http://hl7.org/fhir/risk-assessment-method-example</code> defines the following codes:\n      </p>\n      <table class=\"codes\">\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">\n            <b>Code</b>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <b>Display</b>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <b>Definition</b>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">timi\n            <a name=\"risk-assessment-method-example-timi\"> </a>\n          </td>\n          <td>TIMI</td>\n          <td>Thrombolysis in Myocardial Infarction Risk</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">prism\n            <a name=\"risk-assessment-method-example-prism\"> </a>\n          </td>\n          <td>PRISM</td>\n          <td>Pediatric risk of mortality (PRISM)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">cardiff-t2d\n            <a name=\"risk-assessment-method-example-cardiff-t2d\"> </a>\n          </td>\n          <td>Cardiff T2D</td>\n          <td>Cardiff Type 2 Diabetes Risk</td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
